{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1686-04_063","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"La Vérité. Fable","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", avril 1686 [tome 5], p. 63-72","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"La Fable qui suit a esté trouvée fort ingenieuse. Elle est d’un Gentilhomme de Marseille, dont je vous ay déja envoyé plusieurs Ouvrages galans, que vous avez leus avec plaisir. La Morale renfermée dans celuy-cy pourra estre utile à ceux qui voudront bien ne se point flater."],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":{"value":"LA VERITÉ.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#"},"lb":{},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"FABLE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du temps heureux de Saturne &amp; de Rhée,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Verité digne d’estre adorée,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Faisoit icy-bas son sejour.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les hommes s’empressoient à luy faire la Cour ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais dés que la Discorde affreuse","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Eut infecté tous les cœurs de son fiel,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle fut obligée à chercher dans le Ciel","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Avec la Paix devenuë odieuse,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Une retraite plus heureuse.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les grands honneurs qu’elle receut des Dieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur accueil obligeant, leur entretien aimable,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Le Nectar delicieux","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Qu’elle beuvoit à leur table,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Tout cela fut incapable","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’adoucir le chagrin de son bannissement.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Cent fois le jour, de moment en moment","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  La Terre qu’elle avoit laissée,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Estoit presente à sa pensée.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle se souvenoit d’avoir veu les Mortels","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Prosternez à ses pieds luy rendre des hommages,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Couronner de fleurs ses Images,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et prests à luy dresser de superbes Autels.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Pour se défaire d’une idée","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Si puissante &amp; pleine d’appas,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" En vain son cœur donna mille combats,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Elle en estoit trop possedée,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il fallut se résoudre à descendre icy-bas.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Depuis ce jour fatal qu’elle se vit reduite","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  A suivre la Paix dans sa fuite,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Plusieurs Siecles s’étoient passez.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par le luxe orgueilleux, la Nature changée","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne laissoit plus former que des vœux insensez.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Jugez combien elle fut affligée.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Un Palais riche &amp; spacieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Qui jusqu’au Ciel porte son dome","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  S’offre à ses regards curieux.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Là jadis un couvert de chaume","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Garantissoit des injures du temps","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Des Bergers simples &amp; contens.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  La bure n’est plus en usage,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le Porte-faix n’oseroit s’en vêtir,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Chacun aspire à la pourpre de Tyr,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que chez luy le Marchand a mise en étalage.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le champ qui produisoit une moisson de Blé,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Est ceint d’un vaste Amphitheatre.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  A l’aspect du Peuple assemblé","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Deux Athletes y vont combattre.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle voit dans des Chars pompeusement traisnez","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Par des Chevaux en harnois magnifiques,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Triompher de jeunes Phrinez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour avoir asservy mille cœurs impudiques.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lasse enfin de courir, de voir, de s’affliger,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un Palais, où l’or sur le Porphyre brille,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Elle demande à loger.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Je suis cette mesme Fille","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que vos Ayeux remplis de pieté","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Reveroient avec leur Famille,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[56]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Comme une Divinité,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[57]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Je m’appelle Verité.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[58]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ce nom le Portier par ordre de son Maistre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[59]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Qui parut à la fenestre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[60]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Luy ferma la porte au nez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[61]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En luy disant, partez, vous nous importunez.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[62]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Sans murmurer la pauvreté","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[63]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Obeït, &amp; s’en va de Palais en Palais","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[64]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Mandier une retraite.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[65]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Pareils complimens luy sont faits,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[66]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  A chaque porte on la traite","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[67]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De coureuse &amp; d’indiscrete ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[68]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Elle devient le joüet des Laquais.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[69]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Il suffit qu’elle se nomme","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[70]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Pour essuyer des refus ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[71]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Elle cherche l’homme en l’homme,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[72]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Mais ses soins sont superflus,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[73]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  L’homme d’autrefois n’est plus.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[74]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Cependant la nuit s’avance,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[75]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle ne sçait encore où se refugier ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[76]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A quelques pas de là dans un autre Quartier,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[77]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Elle découvre au pied d’une éminence","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[78]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Une maison de chetive apparence ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[79]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne dois craindre icy, dit-elle, aucun Portier,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[80]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ny des Laquais la detestable engeance,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[81]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Entrons avec asseurance.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[82]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  La Veuve d’un Savetier,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[83]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui malgré soixante ans se piquoit de jeunesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[84]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De ce lieu se dit la Maistresse.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[85]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Sur le nom &amp; la qualité","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[86]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De cette divine Beauté,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[87]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Qui veut estre son Hostesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[88]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De joye &amp; d’amour transporté","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[89]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A cet honneur son cœur est si sensible,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[90]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’elle en perd à l’instant le souvenir terrible","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[91]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De son extrême pauvreté,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[92]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Elle court dans son voisinage","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[93]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Publier sa felicité.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[94]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour acheter des œufs, des herbes, du fromage,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[95]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De la vinette &amp; du pain,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[96]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Avec plaisir elle engage","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[97]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Son pauvre petit Saint Crespin.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[98]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Tout remuë en son voisinage,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[99]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ses enfans empressez travaillent au repas.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[100]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A cet accueil pourtant honneste &amp; favorable","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[101]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  La Dame ne répondit pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[102]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Elle apperceut en se mettant à table","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[103]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que nostre officieuse avoit les cheveux blancs.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[104]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il faut, luy dit elle, ma Mie,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[105]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que vous ayez grand nombre d’ans,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[106]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Sur vos pieds mal affermie","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[107]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Vous marchez à pas chancelans.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[108]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" O Dieux ! vous n’avez point de dents.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[109]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je vous laisse à penser quelle fut la colere","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[110]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que ce discours franc, mais mocqueur,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[111]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Deut allumer dans le cœur","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[112]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  De cette nouvelle Mégere.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[113]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Perdant respect &amp; raison","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[114]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle prend par le bras la Dame trop sincere,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[115]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Luy dit pire que son nom,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[116]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Et la met hors de la maison.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[117]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De cette ingenieuse Fable","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Voicy la moralité ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy que belle, la Verité","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’est pas toûjours agreable.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}]}}}